column18:
Welcome! I appreciate your time to participate in this research. The purpose of this survey is to gather information and opinions on AI-powered Voice Assistants (VAs), which will be used to better understand existing trends, attitudes, and behaviors. The recordings were generated using ChatGPT through a custom Amazon Alexa. 

Your responses will be kept strictly confidential, and feel free to opt out at anytime. The survey should take approximately 5 minutes to complete, and you will need to listen to some audio recordings. Attention checks will be present, please pay attention to the recordings. Do you agree to participate in this survey?

Ive had both good and bad experiences of using Alexa. Ive heard many of my family shouting atan Alexa for getting answers to questions that were totally different to what they were asking so I know Im not the only one. I generally find that and Sirito be useful tools though. I use for timers and weather forecasts along with getting recipes and film information. On the whole I think they do more things right than wrong but can misinterpret what youre asking.
